{"tid":707173,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)亞馬遜迷藏 雷霆喪星 怪獸拆樓","createTime":"2018-06-18T13:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T17:34:48.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"339bbb742d1b46e5c5b045698aaac77ed3d35227","tid":707173,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:06:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=nIQYG1xYKFsWK%2Fp42rwqrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=99e95466\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=nIQYG1xYKFsWK%2Fp42rwqrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0fd619ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=nIQYG1xYKFsWK%2Fp42rwqrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=62ed0262\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/The_Rundown_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F87%2FThe_Rundown_poster.jpg&h=1b49fd23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/70/Tropic_thunder_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F70%2FTropic_thunder_poster.jpg&h=f80736c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://orig00.deviantart.net/dda5/f/2013/043/9/0/the_monsters_of_the_rampage_series_by_animepete2211-d5upvaz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forig00.deviantart.net%2Fdda5%2Ff%2F2013%2F043%2F9%2F0%2Fthe_monsters_of_the_rampage_series_by_animepete2211-d5upvaz.jpg&h=ba16f61a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.賞金獵人貝克（巨石強森）為他的僱主比利去巴西熱帶雨林尋找叛逆離家的兒子特拉維斯（西恩&middot;威廉&middot;史考特），貝克租用了戴克林的飛機和汽車來到巴西熱帶雨林，卻發現康奈紐斯&middot;伯納德&middot;哈奇（克里斯多夫&middot;華肯）非法奴役當地的印第安人為他挖礦淘金。特拉維斯曾經在美國史丹福大學讀書，中途輟學來到這裡尋找印第安文化中遺失的寶物「嘎圖」（一尊神像），他和印地安女孩瑪麗&middot;安娜（羅莎里奧&middot;道森）是好友，兩人都對嘎圖有著強烈的好奇心，兩人都懂葡萄牙語。貝克捉到了特拉維斯之後，激怒了殖民主哈奇，哈奇派遣一支隊伍將對他們窮追不捨，二人在逃亡中遇到了當地印第安人，特拉維斯不肯跟著貝克回美國<br />\n<br />\n2.三位好萊塢巨星傻呼呼地去到東南亞荒蕪地帶拍戰爭片，可是，導演難以控制這班自我本位，喜歡擺架子的演員，於是絕情地將他們遺棄在一個聚集了毒品軍團的隱蔽森林，打算暗地拍攝一個戰爭片真人騷。三位巨星在森林中遇到真正的毒品軍團，以為自己正在演戲，為了爭奪奧斯卡最佳男主角獎，拚命與毒品軍團「對戰」，後來發覺事有蹺蹊，原來自己並非身處拍攝場地，而是真正的戰場！意外被迫面臨一場真正的戰爭，大家唯有假戲真做，硬個頭皮與敵軍對抗<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述靈長類動物學家戴維斯&middot;奧柯耶是反盜獵單位的負責人，當他發現自己心愛的白化大猩猩朋友喬治感染了一種神秘的突變體，而變得相當巨大且具侵略性的野獸。更糟糕的是，一隻名為拉爾夫的紅狼和名為利茲的美洲鱷也遭受了感染。在基因學家凱特&middot;考德威爾博士的幫助下，戴維斯必須拯救喬治，並阻止拉爾夫與利茲襲擊美國的都會地區，並查明到底是誰對這些動物們動了手腳。<br />\n<br />\n9 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=nIQYG1xYKFsWK%2Fp42rwqrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7c38196a\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=nIQYG1xYKFsWK%2Fp42rwqrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ca0163d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e941bdbca1120cee267d221d8ae272af94b3c33","tid":707173,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f160f7f43ee0833210b38e45ba65807ec1e2549","tid":707173,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a0ff21181c58b6a7e67b3a90ebb8f80077a9ed","tid":707173,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T13:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fe0c4084eccbdabed19db5e4e9723dbef6ae55","tid":707173,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7069bbe4ba4f1931ce09765a729ae5fb3027d8eb","tid":707173,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9aef574350201372d6a265b7d407005809527c7","tid":707173,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c384a059b80373bb4af8baa5